name: Am I Cat
description:
Computer gives to cat a fish or a shovel, cat can try predict what this is object.

In start position cat not know what we give him(it is just 1 and 0 digital neutrality/polarity, we can change them it is not have a meaning to be honest) but cat can learning and after some learning cat can choose the fish but not a shovel.

Our game is saying to cat possible it is to eat and healthy it is or not, we can see and we know sure what is fish what is a shovel, and we can help our cat to be healthy too.

*just click say yes or no
